I don't think they want to call it that.

9
00:02:02,095 --> 00:02:04,816
They've been fantastic games to work on.

10
00:02:05,357 --> 00:02:08,999
I'm very grateful to have been involved in these three really,

11
00:02:09,299 --> 00:02:11,640
really beautifully made games.

12
00:02:11,900 --> 00:02:14,642
And I've really just been honored that they chose me

13
00:02:14,662 --> 00:02:16,023
and that they appreciated my music.

14
