00:18:20,937 --> 00:18:23,698
And I decided to do very little with the accompaniment

234
00:18:23,718 --> 00:18:25,638
with the tone part because I didn't think

235
00:18:25,699 --> 00:18:28,279
the accompaniment, I thought if I made it busy,

236
00:18:28,579 --> 00:18:30,620
it would be fighting the other chromatic part.

237
00:18:37,513 --> 00:18:39,454
All right, so that's that.

