00:18:40,515 --> 00:18:42,537
And then here's a look at the chromatic parts.

239
00:18:42,637 --> 00:18:44,999
So this chromatic part is actually quite complex,

240
00:18:45,459 --> 00:18:48,942
but played pianissimo so that it didn't fight it.

241
00:18:49,222 --> 00:18:50,443
But basically it's all strings.

242
00:18:50,523 --> 00:18:52,244
I used a little celesta as well.

