00:19:21,099 --> 00:19:25,761
And I thought, as I was separating them, I thought maybe there's a spot, and one thing

245
00:19:25,801 --> 00:19:30,602
to realize as a composer for a video game is that you never, there's no music, well

246
00:19:30,662 --> 00:19:34,663
there's, not always, but a lot of music can get utilized in different spots.

247
00:19:34,683 --> 00:19:39,025
So I thought, okay, I can deliver both of these to Jim, and he can use this in some

248
00:19:39,065 --> 00:19:42,346
